      "start_time": 19.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "eb722802-30d9-4ffe-a329-55dea1957e3b",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "Good. I was actually calling for you. Um, I'm calling with rentable for an internet listing site. I saw you guys offering some specials, and just wanted to see if you'd be open to a conversation on how we're helping properties connect with renters. Streamline efficiencies, produced costs. I didn't know if that would be a good time."
