      "recording_attendee_id": "8d595fb4-f5d1-4ee9-886d-3a7e92edbb1b",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "Uh It's just something I had in place for the last few months, so I kinda just left it um because I'm not really giving it out to that many, as far as volume of concern honestly. Um But it's just something I haven't played just as a little attractive thing but I don't really need any uh like occupancy else. We've been pretty high fortunately for the last year."
